<li>Strauss, Andrew. <a href="http://www.oneworldtrust.org/documents/taking%20democracy%20global.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.oneworldtrust.org/documents/taking%20democracy%20global.pdf" rel="nofollow">Taking Democracy Global: Assessing the Benefits and Challenges of a Global Parliamentary Assembly</a>. (London: One World Trust, 2005).</li>
